    "text": "i) The singer likes travelling. \u25a1ii) The singer invites the stream to join his song. \u25a1iii) The skylarks usually are in their nests. \u25a1iv) The sound of Blackbirds are sad. \u25a1v) The singer wishes to travel all his life. \u25a1",
