    "bbox": [
      203.56,
      49.65,
      321.45,
      66.0
    ],
    "text": "An Unforgettable Trip",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      70.84,
      453.03,
      87.0
    ],
    "text": "The trip we made to Kataragama during my school holidays was an unforgettable",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      91.65,
      453.02,
      108.0
    ],
    "text": "one. We left home early in the morning and reached Kataragama by the evening.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      112.65,
      453.0,
      129.0
    ],
    "text": "Everybody got out of the van and began to unload the baggage. My uncle got",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      133.65,
      453.0,
      150.0
    ],
    "text": "on to the roof of the van and began to untie the rope so that they could unload",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      154.65,
      453.02,
      171.0
    ],
    "text": "the pots and pans. We took our bags into the room to unpack our clothes. My",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      175.84,
      453.01,
      192.0
    ],
    "text": "mother and aunt went to the kitchen to prepare dinner. After a few minutes I",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      196.65,
      453.02,
      213.0
    ],
    "text": "heard them laughing loudly. They seemed to be enjoying the cooking. As we",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      217.65,
      379.45,
      234.0
    ],
    "text": "were sleepy and tired we had our dinner and went to bed early.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      238.84,
      453.03,
      255.0
    ],
    "text": "The following morning, we woke up early and had a bath in the beautiful Menik",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      259.84,
      453.02,
      276.0
    ],
    "text": "Ganga. Next, we went to the Kiri Vehera and the Kataragama Kovil. We waited",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      280.65,
      452.97,
      297.0
    ],
    "text": "patiently in line at the Kovil to offer a basket of fruits to the Kataragama Deity.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      301.84,
      440.63,
      318.0
    ],
    "text": "We spent the rest of the day walking around the historic city of Kataragama.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      322.65,
      453.03,
      339.0
    ],
    "text": "I was very unhappy to see a lot of garbage left carelessly all around the city.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      343.65,
      453.02,
      360.0
    ],
    "text": "I wish that people were more thoughtful of the environment and were more",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      364.65,
      453.03,
      381.0
    ],
    "text": "careful when they throw garbage. We all came back to the guest house later in",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 9,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      385.65,
      359.59,
      402.0
    ],
    "text": "the evening and packed our bags quickly to go back home.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
